      <title>鲁迪·朱利安尼因抹黑佐治亚州投票站工作人员而必须支付 1.48 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/giuliani-must-pay-148-million-for-smearing-georgia-poll-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿联邦陪审团裁定，唐纳德·特朗普的前高级竞选律师鲁迪·朱利安尼必须向两名 2020 年佐治亚州选举工作人员支付 1.48 亿美元，因为他们宣扬了有关他们的阴谋论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/giuliani-must-pay-148-million-for-smearing-georgia-poll-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称委内瑞拉总统领跑者马查多上诉选举禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/venezuelan-presidential-frontrunner-machado-appealed-election-ban-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府表示欢迎委内瑞拉反对派领跑者玛丽亚·科里纳·马查多决定对阻止她竞选总统的禁令提出异议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/venezuelan-presidential-frontrunner-machado-appealed-election-ban-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:05:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国政府和国有企业加速实施 iPhone 禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-s-apple-iphone-ban-accelerates-across-state-firms-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越来越多的中国机构和政府支持的公司在全国范围内下令员工停止携带 iPhone 和其他外国设备上班，从而启动了一项史无前例的禁令，可能会阻止苹果公司和三星电子公司使用全球最大的移动设备公司的部分地区。市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-s-apple-iphone-ban-accelerates-across-state-firms-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:59:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在加沙地带战斗中误杀三名人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/israel-mistakenly-kills-three-hostages-in-gaza-strip-fighting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防军表示，以色列在加沙地带的战斗中误杀了三名人质，在总统乔·拜登称以色列的轰炸“不分青红皂白”后，引发了人们对其军事行动行为的新质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/israel-mistakenly-kills-three-hostages-in-gaza-strip-fighting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德 (BlackRock) 和道富银行 (State Street) 在众议院 ESG 调查中被传唤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/blackrock-state-street-subpoenaed-in-house-esg-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，众议院司法委员会主席吉姆·乔丹已向贝莱德公司和道富银行发出传票，要求其提供与委员会调查相关的文件，以调查其应对气候变化的努力是否违反美国反垄断法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/blackrock-state-street-subpoenaed-in-house-esg-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 19:27:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫布雷纳德称美国通胀将稳步下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/data-show-us-inflation-poised-to-continue-to-fall-brainard-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫国家经济顾问莱尔·布雷纳德表示，近期的经济数据拓宽了所谓软着陆的范围，越来越多的迹象表明通胀将继续下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/data-show-us-inflation-poised-to-continue-to-fall-brainard-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 18:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汉莎航空将于下个月开始运营返回特拉维夫的航班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/lufthansa-returns-to-tel-aviv-with-flights-from-early-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汉莎航空公司因哈马斯和以色列之间的冲突而暂停了飞往特拉维夫的航班，该公司将于下月初恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班，成为首批返回该国的主要航空公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/lufthansa-returns-to-tel-aviv-with-flights-from-early-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 17:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰放弃对保加利亚加入申根的否决权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/netherlands-drops-its-veto-against-bulgaria-s-schengen-accession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的荷兰政府已同意放弃对保加利亚加入欧盟无护照管制申根区的否决权，使奥地利成为最后的绊脚石。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/netherlands-drops-its-veto-against-bulgaria-s-schengen-accession</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 16:49:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着胡塞武装袭击加剧，航运巨头暂停红海航线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/maersk-tells-all-its-container-ships-to-pause-red-sea-voyages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门沿海胡塞武装分子对商船的不断袭击引发了大范围的贸易中断，世界上一些最大的船东正在评估派遣船员穿越红海是否安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/maersk-tells-all-its-container-ships-to-pause-red-sea-voyages</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:12:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Eskom称南非正在评估是否入股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/eskom-asks-south-africa-to-take-a-stake-to-ease-debt-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非负债累累的国家电力公司 Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. 表示，国家财政部正在评估是否将 160 亿兰特（8.75 亿美元）的救助资金转换为股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/eskom-asks-south-africa-to-take-a-stake-to-ease-debt-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 10:37:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
